org.pepstock.charba.client.intl.enums

Class UTCOffsetConstants

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pepstock.charba.client.intl.enums.UTCOffsetConstants

  • final class UTCOffsetConstants
extends Object
    Contains all UTC offset values used by TimeZone, to avoid to have more instances of the same label.
    Author:
    Andrea "Stock" Stocchero
